description:
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span&gt;An opportunity has arisen for an assistant technical officer to join our friendly ward based team as maternity cover for a fixed term. This role is integral to the success of the ward based team as it supports the safe and efficient supply of medicines to our inpatients as well as helping to facilitate safe and efficient discharges.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hospital pharmacy experience is desirable but not essential as full training will be given. The successful candidate will be working with pharmacists, technicians and ATOs as well as with patients and the wider multi-disciplinary team so a professional and confident demeanor is essential. This relatively new role is constantly developing so this vacancy offers the successful candidate the opportunity to be a part of shaping the role within our team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a small, busy team with a high workload so a willingness to learn and a strong work ethic is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
